ED_Title: Proposed programme  of work and timetable of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee  (Fourth Committee) for the seventy-ninth session of the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: At its 45th plenary meeting, on 7 December 2023, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee),  (Footnote: A/78/430, para.6.) approved the proposed programme of work and timetable of the Fourth Committee for the seventy-ninth session of the Assembly, as set out in the report of the Committee.  (Footnote: A/78/430.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
